		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, the player not being able to flip greatly affects rom, but not vram, unlike what enemies could if they stay in vram. It seems games like shmups would be best suited to the SMS's abilities, because there isn't nearly as much sprite flipping as their would be in just about any other type of game.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
